  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_3' aria-label=\" State of Kerala & Another versus Asianet Satellite Communications Ltd. & Others pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('3','2025','2025_5_2215_2447','2025INSC757'); ><font size='4'> <strong>STATE OF KERALA & ANOTHER<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>ASIANET SATELLITE COMMUNICATIONS LTD. & OTHERS </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 5 S.C.R. 2215</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 757</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010007742025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : B.V. NAGARATHNA<sup style=\"color: #268e97;font-size: 22px;top: 0;\" class=\"tooltip-sup\" data-tooltip=\"Author\">*</sup>, N KOTISWAR SINGH</strong><br> Issue for Consideration The questions for consideration were: 1) Whether appellants- assessees, engaged in broadcasting of signals etc. through television channels to subscribers of those channels, were liable to pay entertainment tax under provisions of respective to Entry 62 &ndash; List II of the Seventh Schedule of the Constitution and also liable to pay service tax under provisions of the Finance Act, 1994 as amended from time to time as a provider of a taxable service namely broadcasting service within the scope and ambit of Entry 97&ndash;List I;<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 22-05-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> CIVIL APPEAL No. 9301/2013</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Disposed off</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 2 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('3','2025','2025_5_2215_2447','2025INSC757','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('3','2025','2025_5_2215_2447','2025INSC757','H'); ><i class='fas fa-file-alt me-2'></i>HTML view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_flip('3','2025','2025_5_2215_2447','2025INSC757');><i class='fas fa-book-open me-2' ></i>Flip view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_pdf('3','2025','2025_5_2215_2447','2025INSC757','N'); ><i class='fas fa-file-pdf me-2'></i>PDF</a></div></div>",
